-- Shares in Monte Paschi suspended after rising more than 7 pct  
-- 
-- Tue Jun 17, 2014 03:13AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, June 17 (Reuters) - Shares in Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> rose more than 7 percent on Tuesday, triggering a limit-up suspension from trading, as the Italian bank's 5 billion-euro stock sale enters its seventh day.

